===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|meticulosus|meticulōsus|full of fear, timid, fearful, terrible, frightful|lang=la}} from {{term|metus||fear|lang=la}} and {{term|-culosus|-culōsus|lang=la}}, extracted from {{term|periculosus|perīculōsus|perilous|lang=la}}.

